tem/flati-responsive-flat-bootstrap-wordpress-theme/6184186" target="_blank">Flati</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/unreal-estate-real-estate-wordpress-theme/5633361" target="_blank">UnrealEstate</a> and <a href="http://www.cssigniter.com/club88/" target="_blank">Club88</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Themes " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Plugins " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Qualia theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/qualia-flexible-multipurpose-theme/5767606" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/qualia.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Qualia is a multi-purpose theme suitable for business, corporate, portfolio and blog. Brand new admin panel with features like color sets, text typography, google fonts and shortcodes.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/qualia-flexible-multipurpose-theme/5767606" target="_blank">Purchase Qualia</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Karma theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/karma-responsive-modern-clean-wordpress/168737" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/karma.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Karma is a simple theme with a clean layout. This theme is suitable for a brandable site and also for personal blog. It comes with the theme options panel, so it’s easy to customize.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/karma-responsive-modern-clean-wordpress/168737" target="_blank">Purchase Karma</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">UnrealEstate</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/unreal-estate-real-estate-wordpress-theme/5633361" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/unreal-estate.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Unreal Estate is a responsive real estate theme which allows you to display a good number of properties, search using many criterias and options, view the information in three different ways and communicate with potential buyers.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/unreal-estate-real-estate-wordpress-theme/5633361" target="_blank">Purchase UnrealEstate</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Flati theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/flati-responsive-flat-bootstrap-wordpress-theme/6184186" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/flati.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Flati is a responsive portfolio WordPress Theme which has been built using the Twitter Bootstrap framework. Some features of Flati are: unlimited sidebars, revolution slider, contact form and shortcodes.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/flati-responsive-flat-bootstrap-wordpress-theme/6184186" target="_blank">Purchase Flati</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Club88 theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/club88-premium-music-wordpress-theme/5740471" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/club88.png" width="590" height="291" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Club88 theme is aimed at clubbers in need for a solution that focuses on what matters most to them. User friendly admin panel allows you to do customizations without knowing any HTML or CSS.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/club88-premium-music-wordpress-theme/5740471" target="_blank">Purchase Club88</a></p>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:84:"http://wpml.org/2013/12/week-compatible-qualia-karma-flati-unrealestate-club88/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:50:"WooCommerce extensions that are multilingual ready";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:47:"http://wpml.org/2013/12/woocommerce-extensions/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"http://wpml.org/2013/12/woocommerce-extensions/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 05 Dec 2013 08:04:20 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:22:"Compatibility Bulletin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"http://wpml.org/?p=302534";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:461:"This week we are glad to announce a list of compatible WooCommerce extensions with WooCommerce Multilingual: Stamps.com, Twilio SMS notifications, Litmos, Kiss metrics, Dwolla, Braintree, Authorize.net, Braintree Transparent Redirect, CyberSource Payment Gateway, CyberSource eCheck SOP Payment Gateway, CyberSource SOP Payment Gateway, Elavon VM payment gateway, Payza Payment Gateway, Realex Payment Gateway (Redirect), Measurement Price Calculator, [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"Dominykas";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11138:"<p>This week we are glad to announce a list of compatible WooCommerce extensions with WooCommerce Multilingual: <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/stamps-com-xml-file-export/" target="_blank">Stamps.com</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/twilio-sms-notifications/" target="_blank">Twilio SMS notifications</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/litmos/" target="_blank">Litmos</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/kiss-metrics/" target="_blank">Kiss metrics</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/dwolla/" target="_blank">Dwolla</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/braintree/" target="_blank">Braintree</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/authorize-net-dpm/" target="_blank">Authorize.net</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/braintree-transparent-redirect/" target="_blank">Braintree Transparent Redirect</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/cybersource-payment-gateway/" target="_blank">CyberSource Payment Gateway</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/cybersource-echeck-sop/" target="_blank">CyberSource eCheck SOP Payment Gateway</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/cybersource-sop/" target="_blank">CyberSource SOP Payment Gateway</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/elavon-vm-payment-gateway/" target="_blank">Elavon VM payment gateway</a>,<br />\n<a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/payza-gateway/" target="_blank">Payza Payment Gateway</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/realex-redirect-payment-gateway/" target="_blank">Realex Payment Gateway (Redirect)</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/measurement-price-calculator/" target="_blank">Measurement Price Calculator</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/sequential-order-numbers-pro/" target="_blank">Sequential Order Numbers Pro</a>, <a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/woocommerce-tab-manager/" target="_blank">Tab Manager</a>.</p>\n<p>These are the first WooCommerce extensions that we reviewed. We will be more than happy to work on other WooCommerce extensions. Let us know what interests you most and we will prioritize them.</p>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Stamps.com</h2>\n<blockquote><p>The WooCommerce Stamps.com extension allows you to select orders to export into an XML format for import into the Stamps.com client. Save time and money by exporting your order information to the Stamps.com client quickly and easily.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/stamps-com-xml-file-export/" target="_blank">Purchase Stamps.com</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Twilio SMS notifications</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Send SMS updates to customers when their order status is updated and receive an SMS message when a customer places a new order.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/twilio-sms-notifications/" target="_blank">Purchase Twilio SMS notifications</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Litmos</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Leverage the e-commerce power of WooCommerce with the easy course creation and management of Litmos to sell your courses online, or give them away for free.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/litmos/" target="_blank">Purchase Litmos</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Kiss metrics</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Add KISS Metrics tracking to your WooCommerce store with one click and start getting actionable metrics today. Easily build a customized dashboard that shows you the metrics you care about, visualize your checkout funnel with sales funnel reports, and watch visitors interact with your store in real-time.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/kiss-metrics/" target="_blank">Purchase Kiss metrics</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Dwolla</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Dwolla is an online payment gateway that works with your financial institution to offer safer, cheaper, and more efficient payment experiences. Transactions under $10 are free, and all others are just 25¢.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/dwolla/" target="_blank">Purchase Dwolla</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Kiss metrics</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Finally, a payment gateway not from the stone age. Braintree offers an all-in-one merchant and gateway solution to process your credit card transactions. Braintree offers unparalleled support and scalability, which is why they are the leader in mobile transactions.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/braintree/" target="_blank">Purchase Braintree</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Authorize.net</h2>\n<blockquote><p>The Authorize.Net DPM Payment Gateway handles all the steps in the secure transaction while remaining virtually transparent, thus simplifying PCI compliance.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/authorize-net-dpm/" target="_blank">Purchase Authorize.net</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Braintree Transparent Redirect</h2>\n<blockquote><p>The Braintree Transparent Redirect Payment Gateway handles all the steps in the secure transaction while remaining virtually transparent, significantly reducing the scope of PCI-DSS.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/braintree-transparent-redirect/" target="_blank">Purchase Braintree Transparent Redirect</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">CyberSource Payment Gateway</h2>\n<blockquote><p>CyberSource for WooCommerce is a gateway plugin that allows you to take credit card payments via CyberSource directly on your site.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/cybersource-payment-gateway/" target="_blank">Purchase CyberSource Payment Gateway</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">CyberSource eCheck SOP (Silent Order Post) Payment Gateway</h2>\n<blockquote><p>CyberSource eCheck SOP (Silent Order Post) payment gateway for WooCommerce.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/cybersource-echeck-sop/" target="_blank">Purchase CyberSource eCheck Payment Gateway</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">CyberSource SOP (Silent Order Post) Payment Gateway</h2>\n<blockquote><p>CyberSource SOP (Silent Order Post) payment gateway for WooCommerce.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/cybersource-sop/" target="_blank">Purchase CyberSource SOP Payment Gateway</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Elavon VM (Virtual Merchant) payment gateway</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Elavon VM for WooCommerce is a gateway plugin that allows you to take credit card payments via Elavon directly on your site, resulting in a completely integrated and seamless checkout process.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/elavon-vm-payment-gateway/" target="_blank">Purchase Elavon VM</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Payza Payment Gateway</h2>\n<blockquote><p>This gateway allows you to safely and securely accept payment from your customers Payza E-Wallet. Customers are automatically redirected to Payza’s secure servers for payment, and redirected back to your site after paying, meaning that you don’t need to spend time installing and managing SSL certificates, and can focus on selling more goods and services.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/payza-gateway/" target="_blank">Purchase Payza</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Realex Payment Gateway (Redirect)</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Realex Redirect for WooCommerce is a gateway plugin that allows you to safely and easily accept credit card payments with Realex, without the need for an SSL certificate or undergoing costly PCI compliance.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/realex-redirect-payment-gateway/" target="_blank">Purchase Realex (Redirect)</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Realex Payment Gateway (Remote)</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Realex (Remote) payment gateway for WooCommerce.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/realex-payment-gateway/" target="_blank">Purchase Realex (Remote)</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Measurement Price Calculator</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Add a calculator to your product pages to calculate the product quantity required by square footage and more.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/measurement-price-calculator/" target="_blank">Purchase Measurement Price Calculator</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Sequential Order Numbers Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>The WooCommerce Sequential Order Numbers Pro plugin allows your store to have sequential, rather than random order numbers.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/sequential-order-numbers-pro/" target="_blank">Purchase Sequential Order Numbers Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Tab Manager</h2>\n<blockquote><p>The Tab Manager gives you complete control over your product page tabs, allowing you to easily create new tabs, share tabs among multiple products, reorder tabs using a visual drag-and-drop interface, and more.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/woocommerce-tab-manager/" target="_blank">Purchase Tab Manager</a></p>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:52:"http://wpml.org/2013/12/woocommerce-extensions/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_expl