e of drains and filters by ochre; and the difficulties of establishing vegetation cover on earthworks and restored land. Off-site problems stem from drainage effluents, earthworks, excavations, and mines. The acid drainage water carries Al released by acid weathering of soil minerals. Our northern part has been suffering for acidity problems for couple of years. Project will try to get rid of it through sub-activity Dolomite treatment.[/accordion]', 'The key framework and programme in Bangladesh to address ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '267-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-01 08:54:40', '2013-12-01 08:54:40', '', 267, 'http://localhost/iapp/267-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
